Alle implementierten Schnittstellen:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class MainScreenVBox extends javafx.scene.layout.VBox
VBox layout for the main screen of the application. This class extends VBox and contains a search field and a MainScreenTableView.
